ound, he explains, it feels different: \\\"The lead up to Tokyo was a bit strange as we could not be in contact with loads of people.\", \"from\": 387, \"to\": 529, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 454, \"end\": 459, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.994005913924172, \"rank\": 0.00603021522398063, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The lead\", \"from\": 439, \"to\": 447}, {\"ngram\": \"contact\", \"from\": 500, \"to\": 507}, {\"ngram\": \"loads\", \"from\": 513, \"to\": 518}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 522, \"to\": 528}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I actually moved my training partner into my house to train during Covid in preparation for Tokyo.\", \"from\": 530, \"to\": 628, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 622, \"end\": 627, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.994005913924172, \"rank\": 0.00603021522398063, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my training partner\", \"from\": 547, \"to\": 566}, {\"ngram\": \"my house\", \"from\": 572, \"to\": 580}, {\"ngram\": \"Covid\", \"from\": 597, \"to\": 602}, {\"ngram\": \"preparation\", \"from\": 606, \"to\": 617}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Now it's a bit more open.\", \"from\": 630, \"to\": 656, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Being able to travel for competitions and training camps, I feel like preparation has gone better, and I feel a lot more relaxed now.\", \"from\": 657, \"to\": 790, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"competitions\", \"from\": 682, \"to\": 694}, {\"ngram\": \"training camps\", \"from\": 699, \"to\": 713}, {\"ngram\": \"preparation\", \"from\": 727, \"to\": 738}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am enjoying the process.\\\"\", \"from\": 791, \"to\": 818, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the process\", \"from\": 805, \"to\": 816}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Tokyo seemed a lonely experience for many athletes, but Woolley has great support for Paris.\", \"from\": 820, \"to\": 912, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 820, \"end\": 825, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.994005913924172, \"rank\": 0.00603021522398063, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 876, \"end\": 883, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morwenstow\", \"score\": 0.687332651590035, \"rank\": 0.3963757260320902, \"text\": \"Woolley\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morwenstow\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morwenstow\"}, {\"begin\": 906, \"end\": 911, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999999982316922, \"rank\": 1.7683017318075753e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lonely experience\", \"from\": 833, \"to\": 852}, {\"ngram\": \"many athletes\", \"from\": 857, \"to\": 870}, {\"ngram\": \"great support\", \"from\": 888, \"to\": 901}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sparring partners are an important part of taekwondo and Woolley is hoping for better results with the help of his support team.\", \"from\": 914, \"to\": 1042, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 971, \"end\": 978, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morwenstow\", \"score\": 0.687332651590035, \"rank\": 0.3963757260320902, \"text\": \"Woolley\", \"types\": [], \"