, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"He might not be able to kick 100% but he is always there to hold pads and motivate me.\\\"\", \"from\": 1282, \"to\": 1370, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"100%\", \"from\": 1312, \"to\": 1316}, {\"ngram\": \"pads\", \"from\": 1348, \"to\": 1352}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Tallaght man's goals have not changed: his aspiration of winning Ireland's first taekwondo medal was cemented by his win over the defending Olympic champion Vito Dell'Aquila last year.\", \"from\": 1372, \"to\": 1560, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1376, \"end\": 1384, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tallaght\", \"score\": 0.9976506303335254, \"rank\": 0.0023506405447346174, \"text\": \"Tallaght\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tallaght\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tallaght\"}, {\"begin\": 1441, \"end\": 1448, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9999902202442453, \"rank\": 9.75961786040331e-06, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}, {\"begin\": 1533, \"end\": 1549, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vito_Dell'Aquila\", \"score\": 0.9999990261692541, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Vito Dell'Aquila\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vito_Dell'Aquila\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vito_Dell'Aquila\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his aspiration\", \"from\": 1415, \"to\": 1429}, {\"ngram\": \"his win\", \"from\": 1489, \"to\": 1496}, {\"ngram\": \"the defending Olympic champion\", \"from\": 1502, \"to\": 1532}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"My goal is the same as it was going into Tokyo,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1562, \"to\": 1620, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1604, \"end\": 1609, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.994005913924172, \"rank\": 0.00603021522398063, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"My goal\", \"from\": 1563, \"to\": 1570}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Realistically I know anyone in that division can come away with the gold medal.\", \"from\": 1621, \"to\": 1701, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"anyone\", \"from\": 1643, \"to\": 1649}, {\"ngram\": \"that division\", \"from\": 1653, \"to\": 1666}, {\"ngram\": \"the gold medal\", \"from\": 1686, \"to\": 1700}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The Olympic champion from Tokyo, I actually beat last year, so I know when I am on form and I am fighting the best I can fight, there is no reason I cant come away with an Olympic gold medal\\\" Woolley has lofty ambitions but insists he is trying not to overburden himself this time around.\", \"from\": 1703, \"to\": 1993, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1730, \"end\": 1735, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.994005913924172, \"rank\": 0.00603021522398063, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 1897, \"end\": 1904, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morwenstow\", \"score\": 0.687332651590035, \"rank\": 0.3963757260320902, \"text\": \"Woolley\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morwenstow\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morwenstow\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"form\", \"from\": 1787, \"to\": 1791}, {\"ngram\": \"no reason\", \"from\": 1841, \"to\": 1850}, {\"ngram\": \"lofty ambitions\", \"from\": 1908, \"to\": 1923}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The expectations are high.\", \"from\": 1995, \"to\": 2022, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The expectations\", \"from\": 1996, \"to\": 2012}]}, {\"sentence\": \"[But] I think I put too much pressure on myself last time and did not really get to enjoy the Olympic experience.\\\"\", \"from\": 2023, \"to\": 2137, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"too much pressure\", \"from\": 2043, \"to\": 2060}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic experience\", \"from\": 2113, \"to\": 2135}]}, {\"sentence\": \"One aspect of the Olympic experience he is relishing is the prospect of having home support, but he jokes that he does not want to know the details.\", \"from\": 2139, \"to\": 2287, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"One aspect\", \"from\": 2139, \"to\": 2149}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic experience\", \"from\": 2153, \"to\": 2175}, {\"ngram\": \"the prospect\", \"from\": 2195, \"to\": 2207}, {\"ngram\": \"home support\", \"from\": 2218, \"to\": 2230}, {\"ngram\": \"the details\", \"from\": 2275, \"to\": 2286}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Family and friends are coming over to see me.\", \"from\": 2289, \"to\": 2335, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Family\", \"from\": 2290, \"to\": 2296}, {\"ngram\": \"friends\", \"from\": 2301, \"to\": 2308}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I do not really have too much involvement in that, I have told my parents to keep that away from me.\", \"from\": 2336, \"to\": 2436, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"too much involvement\", \"from\": 2357, \"to\": 2377}, {\"ngram\": \"my parents\", \"from\": 2399, \"to\": 2409}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I do not want to know too much about it so I can just focus on the sport.\", \"from\": 2438, \"to\": 2512, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 2502, \"to\": 2511}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Just hearing that noise and that support is just going to be amazing and makes the Olympic experience just that little bit better\\\" The first hurdle Woolley has to clear is making weight prior to his first bout, something that is required more frequently in taekwondo.\", \"from\": 2514, \"to\": 2785, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2666, \"end\": 2673, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morwenstow\", \"score\": 0.687332651590035, \"rank\": 0.3963757260320902, \"text\": \"Woolley\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morwenstow\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morwenstow\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that noise\", \"from\": 2528, \"to\": 2538}, {\"ngram\": \"support\", \"from\": 2548, \"to\": 2555}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic experience\", \"from\": 2594, \"to\": 2616}, {\"ngram\": \"The first hurdle\", \"from\": 2646, \"to\": 2662}, {\"ngram\": \"weight\", \"from\": 2694, \"to\": 2700}, {\"ngram\": \"his first bout\", \"from\": 2710, \"to\": 2724}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 2726, \"to\": 2735}, {\"ngram\": \"taekwondo\", \"from\": 2772, \"to\": 2781}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The older you get the more difficult it is,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 2787, \"to\": 2841, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are competing so often.\", \"from\": 2842, \"to\": 2869, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's hard to talk about because it's a way of life, it has always come as a package deal with the sport.\\\"\", \"from\": 2871, \"to\": 2977, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a way\", \"from\": 2909, \"to\": 2914}, {\"ngram\": \"life\", \"from\": 2918, \"to\": 2922}, {\"ngram\": \"a package deal\", \"from\": 2946, \"to\": 2960}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 2966, \"to\": 2975}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A change of category, from 54 to 58 kilograms in 2017, has made things easier but it is still a stressful part of the competition, and he hints at change after Paris.\", \"from\": 2979, \"to\": 3145, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3139, \"end\": 3144, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999999982316922, \"rank\": 1.7683017318075753e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A change\", \"from\": 2979, \"to\": 2987}, {\"ngram\": \"category\", \"from\": 2991, \"to\": 2999}, {\"ngram\": \"58 kilograms\", \"from\": 3012, \"to\": 3024}, {\"ngram\": \"things\", \"from\": 3043, \"to\": 3049}, {\"ngram\": \"a stressful part\", \"from\": 3073, \"to\": 3089}, {\"ngram\": \"the competition\", \"from\": 3093, \"to\": 3108}, {\"ngram\": \"change\", \"from\": 3126, \"to\": 3132}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am not trying to stress about it too much because it can be a stressful part of the competition and I do not want anything like that creeping in.\", \"from\": 3147, \"to\": 3295, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a stressful part\", \"from\": 3210, \"to\": 3226}, {\"ngram\": \"the competition\", \"from\": 3230, \"to\": 3245}, {\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 3264, \"to\": 3272}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am going to focus on my performance and getting the nutrition right, going in fuelled and ready to go.\", \"from\": 3297, \"to\": 3402, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my performance\", \"from\": 3321, \"to\": 3335}, {\"ngram\": \"the nutrition right\", \"from\": 3348, \"to\": 3367}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And after the game we will see what the future holds.\\\"\", \"from\": 3403, \"to\": 3457, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the game\", \"from\": 3413, \"to\": 3421}, {\"ngram\": \"the future\", \"from\": 3439, \"to\": 3449}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Woolley will be in action in Paris on 7 August.\", \"from\": 3459, \"to\": 3506, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3459, \"end\": 3466, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morwenstow\", \"score\": 0.687332651590035, \"rank\": 0.3963757260320902, \"text\": \"Woolley\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/reso